snippet.title: Sword Legacy: Omen - Out Now! (Steam)
snippet.description:
Sword Legacy: Omen is a brand new tactical RPG, set in the candlepunk realm of Broken Britannia. Find out more, over on the official Steam page: bit.ly/SLO-Steam

Note: Sword Legacy: Omen will release on Steam at approximately 5pm BST

Sword Legacy: Omen on Twitter: https://twitter.com/swordlegacy
Sword Legacy: Omen on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/swordlegacy

Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/
Team17 on Discord: discord.gg/team17
